survey_comments: Only SB engine operational when setting the net. Could only attempt 2 sets before we had to leave site to get back in time for eDNA filtering. Second set was botched due to current and fish escaped while pursing.
seine_comments: Currents/eddies caused fish to shoal up often in the net during mesh management. Prior to starting processing; we were going to be hit broadside by severe vessel wake and decided to release the fish preemptively to mitigate additional harm. Therefore; species #s are a very rough estimate based on a couple minutes of observation prior to their release
